snippet.title: THEY WILL NOT STOP Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Prepare for an existential battle in THEY WILL NOT STOP! Pilot diverse starships, unleash devastation, and face an unimaginable threat that devours existence itself. Defend reality in this pulse-pounding spaceship action roguelite. Are you prepared to face the ultimate test? Add it to your Steam Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2515950/THEY_WILL_NOT_STOP/

Featuring a dynamic soundtrack by @Zeanix.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCvUriRbIe_K-IDkj9Cg3pQ
